 pages, requests to \u003ccode\u003ehttps://www.shopify.com/admin/*\u003c/code\u003e redirect the user to \u003ccode\u003ehttps://\u0026lt;shop-name\u0026gt;.myshopify.com/admin/*\u003c/code\u003e, where \u003ccode\u003e\u0026lt;shop-name\u0026gt;\u003c/code\u003e is filled in based on the value of the \u003ccode\u003elast_shop\u003c/code\u003e cookie.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eBecause input validation was missing, any \u003ccode\u003elast_shop\u003c/code\u003e value would be accepted, thereby allowing an open redirect to any domain.\u003c/p\u003e\n"},{"category":"researcher","can_view?":true,"can_create?":false}]}